latestPosts.caption:
Want to become a professional makeup artist?

Join our Basic to Advanced Makeup Course starting from 16th June 2025 and learn everything you need to succeed – from brushes to business!

What this course includes:
	•	Complete Skin Theory – prep, product knowledge, and textures
	•	Base Perfection – foundation, contour, concealer, highlighting
	•	Eye Makeup Mastery – natural, glam, bridal, creative looks
	•	Creative Party Looks – pool party + cocktail makeup
	•	Client Handling – how to deal with all types of clients (even special & high-demand ones!)
	•	Live Demo – how to confidently work on real clients
	•	Photography Skills – how to click stunning makeup shots
	•	Social Media Marketing – grow fast on Instagram, attract more brides & students
	•	Bridal + Editorial Looks – with hands-on practice and portfolio building
	•	Consultation Skills – how to talk like a pro and close clients

Call now to register: 9510608435
Batch starts: 16th June 2025
Seats are limited – book yours before it’s full!
